text: Inguadona is an unincorporated community in Cass County, Minnesota, United States. It is near Longville and Remer along Cass County Road 7 near 28th Avenue NE. Inguadona is located within Inguadona Township and Trelipe Township. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Cass County, Minnesota Category:Unincorporated communities in Minnesota
title: Inguadona, Minnesota
